<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-144] Watching the OST Block I/O Stream (Ch 31)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-144</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In section 31.2.6. Watching the OST Block I/O Stream&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a.  The table is misaligned&lt;br/&gt;
b.  Some row headings read differently than in Lustre 1.8.9 (version specific?)&lt;br/&gt;
discont pages vs. discontiguous pages (same with blocks)&lt;br/&gt;
c.  Should have some live data in the table instead of all &quot;0&apos;s&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
d.  Descriptions of discontiguous pages and blocks should be more descriptive, and ideally indicate what may be causing those numbers.&lt;br/&gt;
e.  Some row headings do not have descriptions.  Should also follow &quot;d&quot; above.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
